{"tid":186260,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 廣東話文化 求大神專家入一入黎","createTime":"2017-04-04T05:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T17:15:54.000Z","uid":66319,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4d8260a5e582511c1de041d8e9e0c21c5301f4","tid":186260,"uid":66319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:33:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟做緊一個研習報告，用英文黎寫(因為係外國讀書) 而我就揀左廣東話文化，希望比外國人認識下香港同廣東話。(同埋教人分清楚支那同香港係唔一樣嘅)<br />\n<br />\n而我就想寫下廣東話嘅歷史，來源，有幾多人講，幾多人嘅母語，廣東話嘅難度同獨特之處。<br />\n但係問題係我上網搵嘅資料好唔同，有啲又話係6000幾萬人母語，又有啲話8000幾萬，都唔知信邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各位幫一幫我，同埋提供一啲有關廣東話嘅網上sources(非wiki)<br />\n多謝哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcea3c5745b145891951a8109f6bb63284c0da5","tid":186260,"uid":66319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:38:41.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"1440abc6e0b56c5865bca756d0a6eccae7ddb833","tid":186260,"uid":66319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:39:13.000Z","msg":"推到有大神專家入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ff4a4d19cac055e6f7e2007939ec7a567fc417","tid":186260,"uid":4184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:49:45.000Z","msg":"呢個topic都幾難搵下喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGoogle scholar 搵下"},{"pid":"2cefd5e8d5cc0744001cbc55d9c890f0802f9c3e","tid":186260,"uid":38778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:37:00.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98f2b8e370d1bddabac5d09902295e7fb81d4d3","tid":186260,"uid":66319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"推呀推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd070101e4d7a85c4ed7daae1b06aae65017625","tid":186260,"uid":73649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,